### Enrichment
Webhook infrastructure is maturing rapidly: Intuit migrating to CloudEvents format (mandatory by May 2026). Azure APIM added native Service Bus policy for event-driven architecture. Hookdeck provides reliable webhook infrastructure. The .notifications/ JSON event bus pattern aligns with modern event-driven approaches. Consider adopting CloudEvents format for the notification JSON schema for interoperability.

